                <p class="pcard-team">Marcel Billingslea, Jana Hazimeh, Sudarshan Sridhar</p>
                <p class="pcard-desc">Expose the infection. Build the immunity. A full-spectrum Bluetooth attack and defense system that weaponizes the trust graph, then inoculates it.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="pcard-actions">
                <a class="pcard-devpost" href="https://devpost.com/software/inocula-weaponize-the-trust-graph-then-inoculate-it" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DEVPOST →</a>
              </div>
            </div>
